    "Widening the annotation to other UMLS groups for devices (DEVI), physiological processes (PHYS) or genes (GENE) would enrich the corpus.",
    "However, according to our experience, other UMLS semantic groups related to concepts (CONC) might cause noise.",
    "It would be rather more adequate to distinguish finergrained concept categories that are not UMLS groups.",
    "Namely, for discriminating drug attributes (administration route, dosage, strength or concentration) and for time expressions (date, duration or frequency), as in other works [81].",
